snippet.title: Tarragona - Part 3 (TRLE) Devil's Bridge - 2001-2002 - by Josep Borrut
snippet.description:
Gameplay recording of Tarragona 3.
This is a long level set, and will likely feature 8 or 9 parts.
Also, due to the nature of recording these parts you may have to turn up the volume on your device.  Apologies.  This has been fixed starting part 7.

Available at:
http://trle.net/sc/levelfeatures.php?lid=190
This is the full series.
